summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Housing and Human Services, authorizing applications to and agreements with the U.S. Department of Health and Human Services and the Washington State Department of Community Development for the expanded operation of Head Start programs and Early Childhood Education and Assistance programs, increasing expenditure allowances in the 1992 and 1993 Budgets of the Department of Housing and Human Services, creating certain positions and making the necessary appropriations therefor.
